invalid type: string "From that day onward, he became known as Dr. Malshan. \nBut success did not make him forget his past. \nHe remembered the nights without electricity. \nHe remembered not being able to buy books. \nHe remembered how lecturers had helped him when he had nothing. \nSo instead of joining a giant corporation or chasing fame, Dr. Malshan returned with a dream:", expected f64ooleanĸ